- Other info:

![image](https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/assets/21674533/f5f5fc5e-bbbc-4bbf-8acc-b08bf6ce6858)

Explicit timeout is not able to overwrite with global timeout. 

Expected state: Ideally expect.poll should wait till 600000 ms instead of 60000.

Expect.poll Method:
```
 async getClusterStatus(idpIPAddress: string, expectedMessage: string) {
        await expect.poll(async () => {
            await this.page.locator("span.ias-icon.ias-icon-reload_refresh_thick").click();
            const text = await this.page
                .locator("div", { has: this.page.locator(`text=${idpIPAddress}`) })
                .locator("div>i").first().getAttribute("title");
            return text;
        }, {
            message: 'Cluster health yet to be turned as GREEN',
            intervals: [1000, 2000, 10000],
            timeout: 600000,
        }).toBe(expectedMessage);
    }
```
